{"tid":2367116,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"電話滋擾兩女警 男女認罪 准保釋候感化報告 下月判刑","createTime":"2021-01-15T05:33:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T06:41:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2d878c1a6bcaded95bb06fd91c73679f6c22c5e6","tid":2367116,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:33:54.000Z","msg":"去年5月市民針對政府強推國安法及國歌法發起示威，當日有警員開設WhatsApp群組分享交通資訊，對話內容遭偷拍兼在網上廣傳，群組內兩名女警事後接獲多通滋擾電話。警方調查後拘控三男一女，繼早前一名男子認罪後，今再有一對男女承認不斷打電話罪，案中分別向兩女警打出7次及8次電話。裁判官劉綺雲為兩人索取感化官報告，押後至下月4日判刑。另一男子則否認控罪，排期至3月24日審訊。<br />\n<br />\n根據通話紀錄，女子曾用其母親登記的電話於32小時內共向兩人打出8次電話，男子則以自己的電話於12小時內打出7次。警方於9月1日拘捕兩人，警誡下黎承認打電話指摘反對示威人士。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210115/AQ36PIH7SZCNRA7AWCE4Q3YHQQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210115%2FAQ36PIH7SZCNRA7AWCE4Q3YHQQ%2F&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFk63eTsi4ka8iUmrXsVTuNg%3D&h=3b4e329d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210115%2FAQ36PIH7SZCNRA7AWCE4Q3YHQQ%2F&h=78006f84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210115/AQ36PIH7SZCNRA7AWCE4Q3YHQQ/</a>"},{"pid":"22d8b6994ba61290984b045af7482e290aa22c0a","tid":2367116,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:37:26.000Z","msg":"呢啲都好告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8c5f89e569de8bfdb62cc8d4103497e5131aae","tid":2367116,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:38:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34690692951ac94876290cd6bf60eb749600a4db","tid":2367116,"uid":89683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T06:03:13.000Z","msg":"12小時打7次<br />\n32小時打8次<br />\n<br />\n都叫不斷打電話？"},{"pid":"88a761da50d8f344657542e840c9ec6bbfbf8482","tid":2367116,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r